title: AVAILABLE SEPTEMBER! 4 RENT :: HUGE BEDROOM NEAR DOWNTOWN ST. PAUL
map_address: Nugent St near St. Clair Ave
posting_body: ['Available 9/1/22!', 'This unit is in the upper level of a duplex on a quiet dead-end street in the West 7th neighborhood in St. Paul.', 'One mile from downtown St. Paul and a half-mile from the Keg & Case Market, the location is ideal with easy access to 35E, I-94, major bus lines, and the shops of West St. Paul.', 'A wonderful grocery store is across the street as well.', 'Original hardwood floors throughout which were recently\xa0refinished.', 'One bedroom and full bath with clawfoot tub.', 'Very large bedroom with enough space for a king size bed & seating or office area.', 'Kitchen has gas stove and room to add a small dining table or island.', 'Back entrance includes a deck overlooking private backyard,\xa0great for summer hangouts!', 'Free laundry facilities included in basement, shared with downstairs tenant.', 'Off-street parking available in exchange for shoveling in the winter/mowing small backyard in summer (all equipment/supplies provided by landlord.)', 'Owner pays water and trash.', 'Tenant responsible for gas and electric.', "Security deposit (one month's rent) due at signing.", 'No smoking allowed.', '\xa0No cats, but pre-approved dogs are welcome with a pet deposit.', 'Non-refundable application fee required.', 'We just bought this duplex in 2020 and have made some beautiful updates to it before listing it to rent.', 'We hope to find some wonderful tenants that will take care of the home and be respectful to neighbors.', 'If interested, please include full name and a bit about yourself/those who would be living with you, serious inquiries can set up a showing.']
